Version 6.0

2008-11-20  Jacques Carette <carette@mcmaster.ca>

	* index.html: Name this version 6.0 from the little accumulated changes
    since 5.0, including renumbering the versions.
	* VERSION: Bump forward.

2008-11-18  Lydia van Dijk  <lvandijk@freenet.de>

	Unify package version numbers.
	* ChangeLog: Augment ChangeLog with the version numbers from
	all 'Makefile' revisions.
	* index.html: Convert document to strict XHTML.  Add a 'keywords'
	meta-tag.  Improve text and code markup.
	Replace the list of changes (Jacques' version numbers) with a
	table of changes according to Lydia's version numbers formerly in
	'Makefile'.

	Revert OCaml version numbers.
	* cc.ml, cc.mli: Revert OCaml version number in the file headers
	from '3.12.0' to '3.11'.  At this point actually everything runs
	with OCaml 3.12.0+dev0.
	* exception.ml, exception.mli: Ditto.
	* io.ml, io.mli: Ditto.
	* monadic_io.ml: Ditto.
	* pa_monad.ml: Ditto.
	* pythagorean_triples.ml: Ditto.
	* test_cc.ml, test_exception.ml, test_monad.ml: Ditto.
	* test_rec.ml, test_syntax.ml: Ditto.
	* utest.ml, utest.mli: Ditto.

2008-11-17  Lydia van Dijk  <lvandijk@freenet.de>

	* pa_monad.ml: Remove links to documents that no longer exist.
	* test_rec.ml: Ditto.

2008-11-13  Lydia van Dijk  <lvandijk@freenet.de>

	Separate version information from 'Makefile'.
	* Makefile: Add sentence-ending period to complete sentences.
	(RM, RMDIR, SED): New variables.
	(clean, distclean, %:%.in): Use new variables.
	(doc): Drop the extension '.html' as the documentation system now
	automatically adds it.
	(VERSION): Get the actual version number from file 'VERSION'.
	(INTERACTIVE-LIBRARIES): New variable.  Drop 'pa_extend.cmo' as it
	does not exist anymore in newer Ocaml versions.  Add 'dynlink.cma'
	to satisfy the reference to 'Dynlink'.
	(top-level): Use variable INTERACTIVE-LIBRARIES.
	* VERSION: New file.

	Add or update copyright information.
	* cc.ml, cc.mli: Add copyright notice including GPL.
	* monadic_io.ml, pythagorean_triples.ml: Ditto.
	* test_cc.ml, test_exception.ml, test_monad.ml: Ditto.
	* test_rec.ml, test_syntax.ml: Ditto.
	* exception.ml, exception.mli: Update copyright year range.
	* io.ml, io.mli: Ditto.
	* pa_monad-camlp4-3.09.ml: Ditto.
	* utest.ml, utest.mli: Ditto.

	* pa_monad.ml: Spice up the documentation by adding hyperlinks to
	the OCaml documentation.  Refer to code in the text more
	consistently.  Insert some linebreaks to make code layout more
	consistent.  Clarify some error messages.
	(quality): Rename local variable.

	* index.html: Tidy; use Un*x-like line ends.


